code: @Bean @ConditionalOnMissingBean public CharacterEncodingFilter characterEncodingFilter() {     CharacterEncodingFilter filter = new OrderedCharacterEncodingFilter().     filter.setEncoding(this.properties.getCharset().name()).     filter.setForceRequestEncoding(this.properties.shouldForce(Type.REQUEST)).     filter.setForceResponseEncoding(this.properties.shouldForce(Type.RESPONSE)).     return filter. }
